      "text": "Background()\n    ↓\nWithCancel( )    → cancelCtx\nWithTimeout( )   → timerCtx\nWithDeadline( )  → timerCtx\nWithValue( )     → valueCtx\nWithoutCancel( ) → withoutCancelCtx",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Background()\n    ↓\nWithCancel( )    → cancelCtx\nWithTimeout( )   → timerCtx\nWithDeadline( )  → timerCtx\nWithValue( )     → valueCtx\nWithoutCancel( ) → withoutCancelCtx",
