      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1205386260,
      "version": 56,
      "versionNonce": 1942441364,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776006582347,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Context.Value 查找顺序是什么？\n从当前节点向上递归查找父链，直到找到 key 或到 emptyCtx。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Context.Value 查找顺序是什么？\n从当前节点向上递归查找父链，直到找到 key 或到 emptyCtx。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
