      "version": 52,
      "versionNonce": 2033389204,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776007032912,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "为什么说 Context 是 “只读不\n写”？\n看一句代码就懂：\nctx := context.Background()\n\n// 看起来像“修改”，其实是：创\n建新 context\nctx2 :=\ncontext.WithValue(ctx, \"key\",\n\"val\")",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "WYB8wdSw8yD1IP4n0xTA-",
      "originalText": "为什么说 Context 是 “只读不写”？\n看一句代码就懂：\nctx := context.Background()\n\n// 看起来像“修改”，其实是：创建新 context\nctx2 := context.WithValue(ctx, \"key\", \"val\")",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
