      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Edge Computing（边缘计算）架构",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Edge Computing（边缘计算）架构",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "dvbxc3bAmEX2z35R9_88e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3474.219411589242,
      "y": 4477.753975611469,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKs",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1431114627,
      "version": 153,
      "versionNonce": 2140411981,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "概述：在 Edge Computing 架构中，媒体流通过位于网络边缘的服务器（例如，CDN 节点、区域性数据中心）进\n行转发和处理，而不是依赖于中心化的服务器。边缘计算通过将计算和存储资源放置在离用户更近的地方，减少了\n延迟并提高了吞吐量。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "概述：在 Edge Computing 架构中，媒体流通过位于网络边缘的服务器（例如，CDN 节点、区域性数据中心）进行转发和处理，而不是依赖于中心化的服务器。边缘计算通过将计算和存储资源放置在离用户更近的地方，减少了延迟并提高了吞吐量。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aPwGy-uLKHONJIChul_OS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3098.219411589242,
      "y": 4567.753975611469,
      "width": 48,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 33925923,
      "version": 153,
      "versionNonce": 1801815725,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "优点：",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "优点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ANBqvarHri_otptGnbC0k",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3378.219411589242,
      "y": 4597.753975611469,
      "width": 608,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKu",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 654986947,
      "version": 153,
      "versionNonce": 196749581,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "通过将计算资源分散到地理位置更接近用户的地方，极大地减少了延迟，提高了性能。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "通过将计算资源分散到地理位置更接近用户的地方，极大地减少了延迟，提高了性能。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QqqFbH2pcTGj40DJu0MPd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3298.219411589242,
      "y": 4627.753975611469,
      "width": 448,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1996062307,
      "version": 153,
      "versionNonce": 1376485229,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "更容易应对大规模用户同时在线的情况，提升系统的可扩展性。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "更容易应对大规模用户同时在线的情况，提升系统的可扩展性。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9S2h2h7Rhq-aHJncRc1MG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3098.219411589242,
      "y": 4657.753975611469,
      "width": 48,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1285667331,
      "version": 153,
      "versionNonce": 1151535565,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "缺点：",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "缺点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kDGn8DgLM-fkbOnDeCk2E",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3338.219411589242,
      "y": 4687.753975611469,
      "width": 528,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 620855715,
      "version": 153,
      "versionNonce": 1687832621,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "需要在多个地理位置部署边缘服务器，这会增加基础设施的复杂性和成本。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "需要在多个地理位置部署边缘服务器，这会增加基础设施的复杂性和成本。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "SynsWr_OYqScXDt9A0lYH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3202.219411589242,
      "y": 4717.753975611469,
      "width": 256,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1497847107,
      "version": 153,
      "versionNonce": 1406843533,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "管理和协调边缘节点可能较为复杂。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "管理和协调边缘节点可能较为复杂。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HJSdBxoEAl7Jem2umXx2Q",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3245.859741745075,
      "y": 4832.414474516527,
      "width": 392.97576904296875,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bKz",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 416396515,
      "version": 134,
      "versionNonce": 991813869,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cloud-based Video Infrastructure (云视频基础设施)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cloud-based Video Infrastructure (云视频基础设施)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vpG_Lq2yR1lkrW0Anqc2k",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3443.989870437081,
      "y": 4865.812898998004,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 590291075,
      "version": 105,
      "versionNonce": 1877818189,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "概述：这种架构使用云基础设施来处理大规模视频通话和直播流。所有的信令、媒体流转发、编解码和处理都通过\n云服务器来实现。云服务提供商可以提供自动扩展、负载均衡和容错等功能，能够支持从小型会议到超大规模会议\n的所有场景。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "概述：这种架构使用云基础设施来处理大规模视频通话和直播流。所有的信令、媒体流转发、编解码和处理都通过云服务器来实现。云服务提供商可以提供自动扩展、负载均衡和容错等功能，能够支持从小型会议到超大规模会议的所有场景。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kJZXyYbCuuW3uOcaqIfBE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3067.989870437081,
      "y": 4955.812898998004,
      "width": 48,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1109268515,
      "version": 105,
      "versionNonce": 1520585133,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "优点：",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "优点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Q1CgyqXw_2qsrnq3oz3BM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3251.989870437081,
      "y": 4985.812898998004,
      "width": 416,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 59579331,
      "version": 105,
      "versionNonce": 476482573,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "高度可扩展，可以动态增加服务器容量以应对大规模用户。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "高度可扩展，可以动态增加服务器容量以应对大规模用户。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MIsQAmdpDWWm771Pt9_LQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3235.989870437081,
      "y": 5015.812898998004,
      "width": 384,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 865774435,
      "version": 105,
      "versionNonce": 1966309997,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "可通过云服务商的基础设施来保证高可靠性和容错性。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "可通过云服务商的基础设施来保证高可靠性和容错性。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "O1Ej7x_Ka-BQ62ieanzk-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3203.989870437081,
      "y": 5045.812898998004,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 378881795,
      "version": 105,
      "versionNonce": 1775414477,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "适合大规模的直播、企业级视频会议等应用。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "适合大规模的直播、企业级视频会议等应用。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LiGFAj15jdxK5v2_naixQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3067.989870437081,
      "y": 5075.812898998004,
      "width": 48,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1660645027,
      "version": 105,
      "versionNonce": 702384941,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "缺点：",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "缺点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "AE9_bCOZuIcgRsX9PwJGD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3219.989870437081,
      "y": 5105.812898998004,
      "width": 352,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2071700035,
      "version": 105,
      "versionNonce": 901619085,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "成本可能较高，特别是当使用大量云计算资源时。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "成本可能较高，特别是当使用大量云计算资源时。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZH2GYElArW-i-Pj2hqvYY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3307.989870437081,
      "y": 5135.812898998004,
      "width": 528,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1760846307,
      "version": 105,
      "versionNonce": 1152148461,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "会受到网络带宽和云服务商数据中心的地理位置限制，可能存在延迟问题。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "会受到网络带宽和云服务商数据中心的地理位置限制，可能存在延迟问题。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CTXPVll8YuCA4LhslMvYh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3175.7035613787443,
      "y": 5203.200722338106,
      "width": 233.72620662429796,
      "height": 20.558573388669856,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 343158147,
      "version": 159,
      "versionNonce": 1790139981,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Decentralized (去中心化) 架构",
      "fontSize": 16.446858710935885,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Decentralized (去中心化) 架构",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Brr-a-zcda_BwU_afq3rg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3446.6455261859332,
      "y": 5230.933210867313,
      "width": 787.3599853515625,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bL9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1094288675,
      "version": 138,
      "versionNonce": 2125204653,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203104,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "概述：去中心化架构是 WebRTC 的一个可能扩展，它使得所有参与者都能在一个去中心化的网络中进行实时通\n信，没有单一的控制服务器。在这种架构中，参与者直接互相通信，可能依赖于区块链或分布式哈希表（DHT）\n来管理信令和媒体流。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "概述：去中心化架构是 WebRTC 的一个可能扩展，它使得所有参与者都能在一个去中心化的网络中进行实时通信，没有单一的控制服务器。在这种架构中，参与者直接互相通信，可能依赖于区块链或分布式哈希表（DHT）来管理信令和媒体流。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "sFeqm6rroICf_WywdPrFw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3076.965533510152,
      "y": 5320.933210867313,
      "width": 48,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1186130115,
      "version": 138,
      "versionNonce": 1077931789,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203104,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "优点：",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "优点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qJ6PCtso7Vb2HVHHRPMQC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3276.965533510152,
      "y": 5350.933210867313,
      "width": 448,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLB",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 176085091,
      "version": 138,
      "versionNonce": 1038648685,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203104,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "消除了对中心化服务器的依赖，增强了系统的容错性和隐私性。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "消除了对中心化服务器的依赖，增强了系统的容错性和隐私性。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1K0QTpNowuWXZA7n78PsD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3196.965533510152,
      "y": 5380.933210867313,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bLC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 980145155,
      "version": 138,
      "versionNonce": 2062503885,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203104,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "无需服务器的媒体转发，可以减少延迟。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "无需服务器的媒体转发，可以减少延迟。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YmbFi6rICisQRu2IZf0Iu",
      "type": "text",
