      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236203104,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. SDP 交换完成\n2. ICE 候选者交换完成\n3. ICE 连接建立（ICEConnectionState\n变为 connected）\n4. DTLS 握手完成\n5. 最终 PeerConnectionState 变为 connected",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. SDP 交换完成\n2. ICE 候选者交换完成\n3. ICE 连接建立（ICEConnectionState\n变为 connected）\n4. DTLS 握手完成\n5. 最终 PeerConnectionState 变为 connected",
