      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. host（主机候选者）\n格式：`udp4 host\n192.168.1.100:54321`\n说明：本地网络接口的直接 IP 地\n址\n优先级：最高（同一网络内最快）",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "UjMteYgo-1XIWq9D8LszR",
      "originalText": "1. host（主机候选者）\n格式：`udp4 host 192.168.1.100:54321`\n说明：本地网络接口的直接 IP 地址\n优先级：最高（同一网络内最快）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
