      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4. prflx（对等反射候选者）\n格式：`udp4 prflx\n192.0.2.1:54321`\n说明：从对端发现的地址（较少\n见）",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "5OLTRD2SuDb_ovvpwzNd9",
      "originalText": "4. prflx（对等反射候选者）\n格式：`udp4 prflx 192.0.2.1:54321`\n说明：从对端发现的地址（较少见）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
