      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "等待ACK超时\n\n\n重试SYN-ACK\n\n\n最终放弃",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "等待ACK超时\n\n\n重试SYN-ACK\n\n\n最终放弃",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Dc1Dj3Y09JjOboDXE4FuJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3409.3103680021845,
      "y": 8322.533182982963,
      "width": 343.6798095703125,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1493859587,
      "version": 113,
      "versionNonce": 1295333539,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "客户端发送SYN后立即断开\n\n\n服务器会重试发送SYN-ACK\n重试次数由 tcp_synack_retries 控制\n最终超时后释放这个半连接",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "客户端发送SYN后立即断开\n\n\n服务器会重试发送SYN-ACK\n重试次数由 tcp_synack_retries 控制\n最终超时后释放这个半连接",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "JTq0WZfZ1zIk3UlDb2wrj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1770.527782535598,
      "y": 7408.350581748827,
      "width": 503.67999267578125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSm",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1297736867,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 911365901,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "拥塞控制就是：TCP自动调节发送速度，别一次性发太多",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "拥塞控制就是：TCP自动调节发送速度，别一次性发太多",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6uphbMHGH-zj46D_V09b-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1752.1059587763984,
      "y": 7472.315831077708,
      "width": 376.8998107910156,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSn",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1050368067,
      "version": 55,
      "versionNonce": 1340877891,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "cwnd = Congestion Window（拥塞窗口）\n\n简单理解：一次最多能发多少个数据包\n单位：字节或包数\n初始值：很小（比如1个包）",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "cwnd = Congestion Window（拥塞窗口）\n\n简单理解：一次最多能发多少个数据包\n单位：字节或包数\n初始值：很小（比如1个包）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OuUd5HtY5w0IA3-zNuvRN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1755.6229238839205,
      "y": 7628.088622057543,
      "width": 463.4798278808594,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSo",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1521309667,
      "version": 84,
      "versionNonce": 359525741,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ssthresh = Slow Start Threshold（慢启动阈值）\n\n简单理解：一个分界线\n当 cwnd < ssthresh：快速增长\n当 cwnd >= ssthresh：慢速增长",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ssthresh = Slow Start Threshold（慢启动阈值）\n\n简单理解：一个分界线\n当 cwnd < ssthresh：快速增长\n当 cwnd >= ssthresh：慢速增长",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Id5CMZ8eA_DeYt_GrsGmq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5789.269200302939,
      "y": 7015.145056292428,
      "width": 507.6998291015625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSp",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 262038403,
      "version": 80,
      "versionNonce": 851684323,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "HTTP/1.0 → HTTP/1.1 → HTTP/2 → HTTP/3演变",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HTTP/1.0 → HTTP/1.1 → HTTP/2 → HTTP/3演变",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "gzBdFfqMVGiAOsioUSz1u",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5781.51472591707,
      "y": 7141.967738212188,
      "width": 653.2994384765625,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSq",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 95222563,
      "version": 43,
      "versionNonce": 226998221,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "HTTP/1.0（1996年）\n特点：每个请求一个连接\n请求1 ──TCP连接── 响应1 ──关闭──\n请求2 ──TCP连接── 响应2 ──关闭──\n请求3 ──TCP连接── 响应3 ──关闭──\n\n时间轴：\n|--连接--|--请求--|--响应--|--关闭--|--连接--|--请求--|--响应--|--关闭--|...\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HTTP/1.0（1996年）\n特点：每个请求一个连接\n请求1 ──TCP连接── 响应1 ──关闭──\n请求2 ──TCP连接── 响应2 ──关闭──\n请求3 ──TCP连接── 响应3 ──关闭──\n\n时间轴：\n|--连接--|--请求--|--响应--|--关闭--|--连接--|--请求--|--响应--|--关闭--|...\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Ia6McVTvtWLcsU_KK2MkJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6503.390255708391,
      "y": 7146.598433030717,
      "width": 531.4598999023438,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1497865923,
      "version": 176,
      "versionNonce": 969553795,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "造成的问题\n\n\n每个请求都要建立新连接（三次握手）\n每个请求都要关闭连接（四次挥手）\n大量时间浪费在连接建立和关闭上\n一个网页有100个资源，就要建立100个连接！\n\n性能对比：\n下载一个网页（100个资源）\nHTTP/1.0: 100 × (三次握手 + 传输 + 四次挥手) = 非常慢",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "造成的问题\n\n\n每个请求都要建立新连接（三次握手）\n每个请求都要关闭连接（四次挥手）\n大量时间浪费在连接建立和关闭上\n一个网页有100个资源，就要建立100个连接！\n\n性能对比：\n下载一个网页（100个资源）\nHTTP/1.0: 100 × (三次握手 + 传输 + 四次挥手) = 非常慢",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "dwselRbJFuXUzSkObsv_b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5780.049326257835,
      "y": 7514.067461350413,
      "width": 706.2593994140625,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSs",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 353160803,
      "version": 160,
      "versionNonce": 1220097581,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "HTTP/1.1（1997年）   核心改进：Keep-Alive（连接复用）\n请求1 ──┐\n请求2 ──┼─ 同一个TCP连接 ─┬─ 响应1\n请求3 ──┤                         ├─ 响应2\n请求4 ──┘                         ├─ 响应3\n                                        └─ 响应4\n\n时间轴：\n|--连接--|--请求1--|--响应1--|--请求2--|--响应2--|--请求3--|--响应3--|--关闭--|\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HTTP/1.1（1997年）   核心改进：Keep-Alive（连接复用）\n请求1 ──┐\n请求2 ──┼─ 同一个TCP连接 ─┬─ 响应1\n请求3 ──┤                         ├─ 响应2\n请求4 ──┘                         ├─ 响应3\n                                        └─ 响应4\n\n时间轴：\n|--连接--|--请求1--|--响应1--|--请求2--|--响应2--|--请求3--|--响应3--|--关闭--|\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Yj_NC6znhvOIoSbFwvYsC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6509.045312537751,
      "y": 7510.949021018284,
      "width": 283.67999267578125,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1808468483,
      "version": 108,
      "versionNonce": 591286051,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "解决的问题\n\n一个TCP连接可以发送多个请求\n减少连接建立/关闭的开销\n性能提升明显\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "解决的问题\n\n一个TCP连接可以发送多个请求\n减少连接建立/关闭的开销\n性能提升明显\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nN9D4NMStwPI8ttD-fQ5F",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6838.598912397856,
      "y": 7502.106975092004,
      "width": 617.2399291992188,
      "height": 675,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSu",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 847303075,
      "version": 32,
      "versionNonce": 1911285901,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "还有的问题:\n1. 队头阻塞（Head-of-Line Blocking）\n请求1 ──┐\n请求2 ──┼─ 同一个TCP连接\n请求3 ──┘\n\n响应顺序必须是：响应1 → 响应2 → 响应3\n\n如果响应1很大，响应2和3就要等着：\n|--响应1(很大)--|--响应2--|--响应3--|\n                 ↑\n              被阻塞了\n\n2.请求必须按顺序发送\n客户端想同时发送请求1、2、3\n但HTTP/1.1要求：\n  发送请求1 → 等待响应1 → 发送请求2 → 等待响应2 → 发送请求3\n\n不能同时发送多个请求\n\n3.Header重复\n\n请求1: Host: baidu.com, User-Agent: Chrome, Cookie: xxx\n请求2: Host: baidu.com, User-Agent: Chrome, Cookie: xxx\n请求3: Host: baidu.com, User-Agent: Chrome, Cookie: xxx\n\n每个请求都要重复发送相同的Header",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "还有的问题:\n1. 队头阻塞（Head-of-Line Blocking）\n请求1 ──┐\n请求2 ──┼─ 同一个TCP连接\n请求3 ──┘\n\n响应顺序必须是：响应1 → 响应2 → 响应3\n\n如果响应1很大，响应2和3就要等着：\n|--响应1(很大)--|--响应2--|--响应3--|\n                 ↑\n              被阻塞了\n\n2.请求必须按顺序发送\n客户端想同时发送请求1、2、3\n但HTTP/1.1要求：\n  发送请求1 → 等待响应1 → 发送请求2 → 等待响应2 → 发送请求3\n\n不能同时发送多个请求\n\n3.Header重复\n\n请求1: Host: baidu.com, User-Agent: Chrome, Cookie: xxx\n请求2: Host: baidu.com, User-Agent: Chrome, Cookie: xxx\n请求3: Host: baidu.com, User-Agent: Chrome, Cookie: xxx\n\n每个请求都要重复发送相同的Header",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "t3Igtlk4J51f-kRO66zbm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5790.514622633084,
      "y": 8223.018495987768,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 550,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 442279235,
      "version": 119,
      "versionNonce": 1636725443,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "HTTP/2（2015年）\n核心改进：多路复用（Multiplexing）\n请求1 ──┐\n请求2 ──┼─ 同一个TCP连接 ─┬─ 响应1\n请求3 ──┤                         ├─ 响应2\n请求4 ──┘                         ├─ 响应3\n                                        └─ 响应4\n\n关键：可以同时发送多个请求，响应可以乱序返回！\n\n时间轴：\n|--请求1,2,3,4同时发送--|--响应可以乱序返回--|\n\nHTTP/2的架构：\nHTTP/2 Stream（流）\n  ├─ Stream 1: 请求1 → 响应1\n  ├─ Stream 2: 请求2 → 响应2\n  ├─ Stream 3: 请求3 → 响应3\n  └─ Stream 4: 请求4 → 响应4\n\n所有Stream共享一个TCP连接\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HTTP/2（2015年）\n核心改进：多路复用（Multiplexing）\n请求1 ──┐\n请求2 ──┼─ 同一个TCP连接 ─┬─ 响应1\n请求3 ──┤                         ├─ 响应2\n请求4 ──┘                         ├─ 响应3\n                                        └─ 响应4\n\n关键：可以同时发送多个请求，响应可以乱序返回！\n\n时间轴：\n|--请求1,2,3,4同时发送--|--响应可以乱序返回--|\n\nHTTP/2的架构：\nHTTP/2 Stream（流）\n  ├─ Stream 1: 请求1 → 响应1\n  ├─ Stream 2: 请求2 → 响应2\n  ├─ Stream 3: 请求3 → 响应3\n  └─ Stream 4: 请求4 → 响应4\n\n所有Stream共享一个TCP连接\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HoAHnrspjkORL4tOKrNEM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6270.7154012593255,
      "y": 8228.261218761303,
      "width": 464.7999267578125,
      "height": 675,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 717030627,
      "version": 230,
      "versionNonce": 450449133,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "解决的问题\n\n1. 解决队头阻塞\n请求1 ──┐\n请求2 ──┼─ 同一个TCP连接\n请求3 ──┘\n\n响应1很大，但响应2、3可以先返回：\n|--响应2--|--响应3--|--响应1(很大)--|\n\n\n2. 解决请求必须按顺序发送\n可以同时发送请求1、2、3、4\n不用等待响应\n\n3. Header压缩\n使用HPACK算法压缩Header\n相同的Header只发送一次，后续请求只发送差异部分\n\n4. 二进制分帧\nHTTP/1.1: 文本格式\nGET / HTTP/1.1\\r\\nHost: baidu.com\\r\\n...\n\nHTTP/2: 二进制格式\n[帧头][帧体][帧头][帧体]...\n更高效，更容易解析\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "解决的问题\n\n1. 解决队头阻塞\n请求1 ──┐\n请求2 ──┼─ 同一个TCP连接\n请求3 ──┘\n\n响应1很大，但响应2、3可以先返回：\n|--响应2--|--响应3--|--响应1(很大)--|\n\n\n2. 解决请求必须按顺序发送\n可以同时发送请求1、2、3、4\n不用等待响应\n\n3. Header压缩\n使用HPACK算法压缩Header\n相同的Header只发送一次，后续请求只发送差异部分\n\n4. 二进制分帧\nHTTP/1.1: 文本格式\nGET / HTTP/1.1\\r\\nHost: baidu.com\\r\\n...\n\nHTTP/2: 二进制格式\n[帧头][帧体][帧头][帧体]...\n更高效，更容易解析\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "m-fvT-BW_V0loooaDJlxI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6841.31142481307,
      "y": 8224.709671209966,
      "width": 402.34480701882546,
      "height": 225.4509800592534,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2066772099,
      "version": 48,
      "versionNonce": 358163043,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "还有的问题:\nTCP是有序的，如果一个包丢失：\n|--包1--|--包2(丢失)--|--包3--|--包4--|\n\nTCP要等包2重传，包3、4才能被应用层使用\n即使HTTP/2可以乱序，TCP也要等\n\n这是TCP的特性，HTTP/2无法解决\n",
      "fontSize": 20.040087116378082,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "还有的问题:\nTCP是有序的，如果一个包丢失：\n|--包1--|--包2(丢失)--|--包3--|--包4--|\n\nTCP要等包2重传，包3、4才能被应用层使用\n即使HTTP/2可以乱序，TCP也要等\n\n这是TCP的特性，HTTP/2无法解决\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GQPFjiQ0snWHoGFCAgMH1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5792.351703168573,
      "y": 8959.70105483801,
      "width": 402.51983642578125,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 762669091,
      "version": 26,
      "versionNonce": 1644882253,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "HTTP/3（2022年）\n核心改进：基于QUIC协议（替代TCP）\nHTTP/1.1: HTTP → TCP → IP\nHTTP/2:   HTTP → TCP → IP\nHTTP/3:   HTTP → QUIC → UDP → IP\n                ↑\n            不再用TCP！\n为什么要替换TCP？\n\n因为TCP的问题：\n\nTCP队头阻塞（即使HTTP/2也解决不了）\nTCP握手慢（三次握手）\nTCP是内核实现，改进困难",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HTTP/3（2022年）\n核心改进：基于QUIC协议（替代TCP）\nHTTP/1.1: HTTP → TCP → IP\nHTTP/2:   HTTP → TCP → IP\nHTTP/3:   HTTP → QUIC → UDP → IP\n                ↑\n            不再用TCP！\n为什么要替换TCP？\n\n因为TCP的问题：\n\nTCP队头阻塞（即使HTTP/2也解决不了）\nTCP握手慢（三次握手）\nTCP是内核实现，改进困难",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "sxajv4-ud4bVWTCKkelFe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6273.20919134759,
      "y": 8952.571590665988,
      "width": 403.99993896484375,
      "height": 675,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bSz",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 662334403,
      "version": 71,
      "versionNonce": 1198317059,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "QUIC的优势：\n\n1. 解决TCP队头阻塞\nQUIC在应用层实现可靠传输\n不依赖TCP的有序性\n包丢失只影响那个Stream，其他Stream继续\n\n|--包1--|--包2(丢失)--|--包3--|--包4--|\n         ↑\n    只有Stream2等待重传\n    Stream3、4继续处理\n2. 0-RTT连接建立\nTCP: 三次握手 = 1.5 RTT\nQUIC: 可以在第一个包就发送数据 = 0 RTT\n\n第一次连接：1 RTT（握手+数据）\n后续连接：0 RTT（直接发数据）\n3. 连接迁移\n\n你在WiFi上下载文件\n切换到4G网络\nTCP: 连接断开，要重新建立\nQUIC: 连接继续，无缝切换\n4. 更好的丢包恢复\n\nTCP: 丢包 → 超时 → 重传（慢）\nQUIC: 丢包 → 立即重传（快）",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "QUIC的优势：\n\n1. 解决TCP队头阻塞\nQUIC在应用层实现可靠传输\n不依赖TCP的有序性\n包丢失只影响那个Stream，其他Stream继续\n\n|--包1--|--包2(丢失)--|--包3--|--包4--|\n         ↑\n    只有Stream2等待重传\n    Stream3、4继续处理\n2. 0-RTT连接建立\nTCP: 三次握手 = 1.5 RTT\nQUIC: 可以在第一个包就发送数据 = 0 RTT\n\n第一次连接：1 RTT（握手+数据）\n后续连接：0 RTT（直接发数据）\n3. 连接迁移\n\n你在WiFi上下载文件\n切换到4G网络\nTCP: 连接断开，要重新建立\nQUIC: 连接继续，无缝切换\n4. 更好的丢包恢复\n\nTCP: 丢包 → 超时 → 重传（慢）\nQUIC: 丢包 → 立即重传（快）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "lhelXbhMknjDFwtORpoIv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2210.0567210178597,
      "y": 9245.170471375264,
      "width": 620.1610107421875,
      "height": 101.47533397430384,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bT0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 224263011,
      "version": 98,
      "versionNonce": 1490696109,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776236254608,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TCP的超时重传机制\n\n发送数据后，等待一段时间没收到ACK，就重新发送",
      "fontSize": 27.060089059814356,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TCP的超时重传机制\n\n发送数据后，等待一段时间没收到ACK，就重新发送",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
